{"tid":1989701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共宜家咁心急 係咪因為知遲早我地都會贏","createTime":"2020-04-26T07:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T02:12:28.000Z","uid":132587,"like":303,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"82e56f0c93cfb4742d966a1787963af298b1605d","tid":1989701,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"過多十年二十年可能再耐d<br />\n班廢老廢中死撚曬<br />\n候生既我地開始變中佬師奶 <br />\n宜家中學果班開始出黎社會擔大旗<br />\n<br />\n黃營開始dominate成個社會主流<br />\n到時分分鐘黃藍82 <br />\n議價能力同大氣侯就唔會好似今日咁<br />\n仲有梁天琦到時40幾50歲夠曬火候<br />\n<br />\n今年狗隊招聘少人到要登報宣傳<br />\n形象大家都知無得挽回<br />\n過左幾年十年分分鐘真警犬仲多過人形警犬<br />\n未聽過一個地方警隊民望keep住咁低都可以做到軍政府<br />\n佢地威多呢一兩年 中共應該好快覺得唔對路<br />\n<br />\n政府係咪預見黎緊我地威脅愈黎愈大<br />\n所以先咁急要赤化香港?"},{"pid":"eba19784c5707c68ca8909a39fd65025e7171e32","tid":1989701,"uid":200070,"like":181,"dislike":6,"score":175,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"傻啦 而家好多大陸人洗血 成個中環都控制曬"},{"pid":"7959049cbb23cc6c85bda963448cf26a1d221ae8","tid":1989701,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"係知佢的好快就輸&amp;被清算"},{"pid":"2803fff200e3f8ea4693e39a10105b5c832b3ef8","tid":1989701,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92c3b99132d135c1d4b477ee4b9b898d66555a6","tid":1989701,"uid":42691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"十年廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116a8c839ebc82b9baca51198bdc04e2071c7737","tid":1989701,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf8c210ffbc4724cb6ed0dc7cf2c5791943baf","tid":1989701,"uid":137493,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a